'''Bob Sharples''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Wins===

* [[Gold Cup (bridge)|Gold Cup]] (7) 195, 1962, 1966, 1967, 1968, 1970, 1979 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (7)
** 0 (7) 195, 1962, 1966, 1967, 1968, 1970, 1979 

===Runners-up===

* [[Gold Cup (bridge)|Gold Cup]] (5) 1955, 1957, 1960, 1964, 1969 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (5)
** 0 (5) 1955, 1957, 1960, 1964, 1969 

